parameters: (Well, um.... That's how it turned out.)

Well, how should I put it... I was 'incompetent'. If only I could
have done better... Or perhaps... I might have been able to reach
a different outcome.

No, it might have been difficult. I had no room to intervene with
my own abilities... Still, I can't help but think about it.
...However, there is one thing that brings salvation.
